text: Morad Zemouri (born March 3, 1993) is a Qatari judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 73 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Dirk Van Tichelt. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Qatari male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Qatar Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics
